metadata.name: Unbreakable UKR
metadata.description:
Ukraine needs our help!

This animation was created to support the humanitarian efforts in Ukraine. All proceeds of the auction will go to Save the Children Australia.

Save the Children is a trusted global organisation founded in 1919 in the UK.

You can learn more about them and also make smaller donations by going to www.savethechildren.org

_

March 2022
10 frame infinite loop
12 fps
1080x1080 px
